EECS494 p3.

This game need 4 players with (4) controllers.
We tested our game (only) using 3 PS4 controllers and 1 Xbox controller.
Contact us if any issue related with input occurs.

Left Stick: Character movement / Adjust direction the corresponding object controlled by gear (when sitting on gear)
Red Gear: Weapon Gear (Stick to adjust direction, Press B (xbox) or O (ps4) to attack)
Blue Gear: Submarine Movement Gear (Stick to move)
Green Gear: Shield Control Gear (Stick to move shield, Press B (in xbox) or O (in ps4) to open a bubble shield)


